p of production of the coates csrv industrial electric power natural gas generators may start very soon in china  the sixth largest manufacturer in china signed a confidential agreement with coates power ltd china sep   at  am et on marketwired coates international ltd and coates power ltd china are working on a daily basis with the chinese to conclude a transaction for the rampup of production operations in china  management expects to conclude the transaction in the next three weeks update aug   at  am et on marketwired coates international ltd is in negotiations covering a number of transactions with some of the largest companies in the world  company president and ceo mr george j coates and mr nicholas kontonicolas coo of the coates organization worldwide are working closely on a daily basis to prioritize and expedite the conclusion of some of these transactions  shareholders update aug   at  am et on marketwired coates international ltd received an agreement from chinabased fujian mingyan cummins engine and generator manufacturer agreeing to manufacture engines and generator sets not to include the csrv heads poppet valves push rods rockers etc  coates will be responsible for integrating the coates csrv patented green engine heads and spherical valve assembly to complete the manufacturing process aug   at  am et on marketwired coates international ltds liaison agent to china mr james pang reported to the company yesterday that the chinese delegation that visited the coates headquarters a few weeks ago have requested a worldwide exclusive license to make use and manufacture the coates patented csrv green engine and generator system technology shareholders update aug   at  am et on marketwired george j coates purchases a further  shares of common stock from coates international ltd aug   at  am et on marketwired mr nick kontonicolas appointed coo of the coates organization worldwide operations including coates power ltd china and coates hydrogen power ltd usa jul   at  am et on marketwired coates international ltd coates international ltd engages in the design and development technologies that evolve the standard combustion engine its patent coates spherical rotary valve system technology is designed to operate in pistondriven internal combustion engines of many types its technology and applications appeal to number of different geographic and product markets including automobiles light trucks heavy trucks machinery railroads marine engines military equipment light aircraft helicopters lawn mowers snowmobiles and jet skis the company was founded by george j coates on december   and is headquartered in wall township nj see full profile competitors name chg  market cap twin disc inc  m borgwarner inc  b cummins inc  b huntsman corp  b competitor data provided by partner content trending tickers powered by fb  amzn  twtr  clf  amd  advanced search stocks columns authors topics no results found video center learn morestoryful a division of news corp which owns marketwatch is a leading social media services company headquartered in dublin ireland storyful combines world class journalism with industryleading technology to discover verify and acquire original content and provide the ontheground sources news and media organizations need to tell the stories that matter to their audience stocks index  markets index bulletin investor alert new york markets close in market snapshot winners and losers stocks rates funds bonds benchmarks real estate investment trusts futures american depository receipt stocks exchange traded notes warrants indexes exchange traded funds currencies crypto currencies browse stocks stocks az abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyzother browse by location argentina australia austria bahamas bahrain belgium bermuda botswana brazil british virgin islands canada cayman islands chile china colombia curacao cyprus czech republic denmark egypt estonia finland france germany gibraltar greece hong kong hungary iceland india indon