l efficiency and power generation and reducing harmful emissions and longterm maintenance costs   coates international was organized on the nd of december  and reorganized in  and existing under and by virtue of the general corporation law of the state of delaware usa is a fully reporting public company whose shares are traded on the otc bulletin board under the symbol cotecoates internationals research and development facility is a  sq ft complex situated on  acres of land site valued at approximately  million coates international has significant intangible assets includinga large number of highly valuable patents eighteen in usa and over one hundred worldwide for combustion engines and new technologies relating to combustion enginesa steam turbine engine valve patenta self adjusting wheel bearing patentconcepts in testing not yet patentedlarge numbers of working prototypesa pulse detonation rocket engine certificationscoates international ltd is a member in good standing of both the better business bureau of new jersey and the electrical generating systems association click on either certificate image to the right for fullsized view all rights reserved   coates international ltd      terms of use      privacy policy      website by nw design coates international ltd ✕ todays stock market news and analysis  nasdaqcom hot topics etfs  smart portfolio  currencies  online broker center search home  stock market news todays stock market news  analysis the metrics behind facebooks monster second quarter by motley fool expectations were high and results didnt disappoint britain to ban fossil fuel vehicles by  by oilpricecom they will instead be replaced by electric vehicles amazon amzn nd quarter earnings what to expect by richard saintvilus investors expectations are flying high gilead sciences boosts its fullyear outlook by motley fool the boost is thanks to their strongerthanexpected hepatitis c drug sales latest news videos jeff bezos tops worlds richest lis mortgage